{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"bdf2f52eb3","title":"关于扩大反内战宣传及建立云、贵、川农村据点的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"78a49bb7d4","index":0,"year":1945,"month":7,"day":22,"articleId":"bdf2f52eb3"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji20","name":"毛泽东全集第20卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji20.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji20":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"22b3f36e01","type":"paragraph","text":"关于扩大反内战宣传及建立云、贵、川农村据点的指示”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"bdf2f52eb3"},{"id":"f5d94cba26","type":"paragraph","text":"（1945年7月22日）徐、张”蒋一切布置都是准备反共的，内战危机空前产重。要求：（一）望将延安反内战新闻在大后方设法传播。这些新闻的措辞将使中间旅认为太尖锐，但日后将证明我们意见之正确性。（二）望用最大注意力布置云、贵、川三省农村据点，准备将来打游击，不便我党在国民党发动内战时处于完全拨打与束手无策的地位，现在就应派人去领导贵州等处的民变","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"bdf2f52eb3"},{"id":"58144e1937","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"bdf2f52eb3"},{"id":"4fa57b1d06","type":"paragraph","text":"七月二十二日口这是毛泽东关干扩大反内我宣传及建立云、贵、川农村提点给染[2]徐，指徐冰（1903-1972）.河北南宫人：张，指张明，即刘少文","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"bdf2f52eb3"}],"page":{"id":"aa77853d7b","publicationId":"maoquanji20","articleId":"bdf2f52eb3","start":186,"end":186}}}},"__N_SSG":true}